                        <h2 class="text-lg md:text-2xl font-bold mb-6 md:mb-8 post-contents__ttl">
                從東京出發可以當日往返的4個滑雪場!巴士路線有介紹！              </h2>
              <ul class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3 post-contents__info">
                <li>
                                      <ul class="flex flex-wrap text-sm -mx-2 post-categories">
                      <li class="relative px-2"><a href="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/zh-hant/entertainment-zh-hant/">Entertainment</a></li><li class="relative px-2"><a href="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/zh-hant/nature-zh-hant/">Nature</a></li><li class="relative px-2"><a href="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/zh-hant/%e6%9c%aa%e5%88%86%e9%a1%9e/">未分類</a></li>                    </ul>
                                  </li>
                <li>
                  <span class="inline-block text-gray-400 text-sm"><time>November 12, 2021</time></span>
                </li>
              </ul>
                            <div class="addtoany_shortcode"><div class="a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_32 addtoany_list" data-a2a-url="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/zh-hant/%e6%9c%aa%e5%88%86%e9%a1%9e/2466/" data-a2a-title="從東京出發可以當日往返的4個滑雪場!巴士路線有介紹！"><a class="a2a_button_facebook" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fjapanbusonline.com%2Fbus-repo%2Fzh-hant%2F%25e6%259c%25aa%25e5%2588%2586%25e9%25a1%259e%2F2466%2F&amp;linkname=%E5%BE%9E%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%95%B6%E6%97%A5%E5%BE%80%E8%BF%94%E7%9A%844%E5%80%8B%E6%BB%91%E9%9B%AA%E5%A0%B4%21%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9%EF%BC%81" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_twitter" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fjapanbusonline.com%2Fbus-repo%2Fzh-hant%2F%25e6%259c%25aa%25e5%2588%2586%25e9%25a1%259e%2F2466%2F&amp;linkname=%E5%BE%9E%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%95%B6%E6%97%A5%E5%BE%80%E8%BF%94%E7%9A%844%E5%80%8B%E6%BB%91%E9%9B%AA%E5%A0%B4%21%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9%EF%BC%81" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_email" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/email?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fjapanbusonline.com%2Fbus-repo%2Fzh-hant%2F%25e6%259c%25aa%25e5%2588%2586%25e9%25a1%259e%2F2466%2F&amp;linkname=%E5%BE%9E%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%95%B6%E6%97%A5%E5%BE%80%E8%BF%94%E7%9A%844%E5%80%8B%E6%BB%91%E9%9B%AA%E5%A0%B4%21%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9%EF%BC%81" title="Email" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_dd addtoany_share_save addtoany_share" href="https://www.addtoany.com/share"></a></div></div>              <div class="my-6 md:my-8">
                                  <div>
                    <p>冬季運動的代表項目滑雪和單板滑雪。隨著冬天的臨近，今年去哪個滑雪場遊玩的人應該也不少吧?這次介紹了從東京都內當天來回就能輕松去的4個推薦的滑雪場。而且，「雖然沒有駕照，但是想去滑雪!」為了「用疲憊的身體在雪地上開車有點……」這樣的人，我們嚴格挑選了公共汽車和電車也能去的地方。請務必作為選擇滑雪場的參考哦。</p>
                                          <img width="1920" height="1444" src="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22313078_m-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22313078_m-1.jpg 1920w, https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22313078_m-1-300x226.jpg 300w, https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22313078_m-1-1024x770.jpg 1024w, https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22313078_m-1-768x578.jpg 768w, https://japanbusonline.com/bus-repo/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22313078_m-1-1536x1155.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" />                                        <nav class="py-4 md:py-6 px-6 md:px-12 my-8 heading">
